statements: SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformance ORDER BY algorithm_id DESC
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_metric FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE index_used = true
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_metric FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE algorithm_name = 'Sort'
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE performance_metric LIKE '%time%'
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_metric FROM AlgorithmPerformance ORDER BY algorithm_name ASC
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE algorithm_id = 5 AND index_used = true;
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_metric FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE algorithm_id IN (1, 2, 3) ORDER BY algorithm_id DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT algorithm_name, performance_metric FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE index_used = false ORDER BY performance_metric ASC, algorithm_name DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_metric FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE algorithm_name LIKE 'A%' OR algorithm_name LIKE '%B' AND index_used = true;
SELECT algorithm_name, COUNT(*) AS total_count FROM AlgorithmPerformance GROUP BY algorithm_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY total_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformanceTrack;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_time FROM AlgorithmPerformanceTrack;
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name, execution_time FROM AlgorithmPerformanceTrack WHERE algorithm_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM IndexOptimization;
SELECT index_id, optimizer_name, optimization_metric FROM IndexOptimization;
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformanceTrack;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_time FROM AlgorithmPerformanceTrack WHERE execution_time > 10 ORDER BY execution_time DESC;
SELECT AVG(execution_time) AS avg_execution_time, MAX(execution_time) AS max_execution_time FROM AlgorithmPerformanceTrack;

SELECT AlgorithmPerformanceTrack.algorithm_id, AlgorithmPerformanceTrack.algorithm_name, IndexOptimization.optimizer_name, IndexOptimization.optimization_metric FROM AlgorithmPerformanceTrack JOIN IndexOptimization ON AlgorithmPerformanceTrack.algorithm_id = IndexOptimization.algorithm_id;
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformanceTrack WHERE algorithm_name LIKE 'A%' ORDER BY execution_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM Algorithm_Performance;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_time FROM Algorithm_Performance ORDER BY execution_time DESC;
SELECT query_text, execution_time FROM Query_Logs WHERE execution_time > 5;
SELECT index_name, index_size FROM Index_Statistics WHERE index_size < 100000 ORDER BY index_size ASC;
SELECT * FROM Algorithm_Performance JOIN Index_Statistics ON Algorithm_Performance.algorithm_id = Index_Statistics.algorithm_id;
SELECT * FROM Algorithm_Performance ORDER BY execution_time DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_time FROM Algorithm_Performance WHERE algorithm_id = 1;
SELECT index_id, index_name, index_size FROM Index_Statistics WHERE last_updated_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY index_size DESC;
SELECT * FROM Query_Logs WHERE execution_time > 5 AND timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-02-01 00:00:00';

SELECT algorithm_name, COUNT(log_id) AS num_queries FROM Algorithm_Performance INNER JOIN Query_Logs ON Algorithm_Performance.algorithm_id = Query_Logs.algorithm_id GROUP BY algorithm_name ORDER BY num_queries DESC;
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE algorithm_id = 1
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_time FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE performance_rating > 5 ORDER BY execution_time ASC
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name, performance_rating FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE performance_rating IS NOT NULL ORDER BY algorithm_name DESC
SELECT AVG(execution_time) AS avg_execution_time, MAX(performance_rating) AS max_rating FROM AlgorithmPerformance
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE algorithm_id = (SELECT MIN(algorithm_id) FROM AlgorithmPerformance)
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE performance_rating > 3 ORDER BY execution_time DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, execution_time, performance_rating FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE algorithm_id = 5;
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_rating FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE execution_time < 0.5 ORDER BY algorithm_name;
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name, execution_time, performance_rating FROM AlgorithmPerformance WHERE performance_rating IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmPerformance ORDER BY performance_rating DESC, execution_time;
SELECT * FROM algorithm_performance;
SELECT algorithm_name, performance_score FROM algorithm_performance WHERE execution_time > 10;
SELECT id, execution_time FROM algorithm_performance ORDER BY execution_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM algorithm_metrics WHERE metric_value < 0.5;
SELECT id, algorithm_id, metric_name FROM algorithm_metrics WHERE metric_name LIKE '%accuracy%';
SELECT * FROM algorithm_performance WHERE performance_score > 80 ORDER BY execution_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT algorithm_name, AVG(execution_time) AS avg_execution_time FROM algorithm_performance GROUP BY algorithm_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;
SELECT algorithm_name, SUM(performance_score) AS total_score FROM algorithm_performance GROUP BY algorithm_name ORDER BY total_score DESC;
SELECT algorithm_id, COUNT(*) AS total_metrics FROM algorithm_metrics GROUP BY algorithm_id HAVING total_metrics > 1;
SELECT index_name, AVG(total_operations) AS avg_operations FROM index_statistics GROUP BY index_name ORDER BY avg_operations DESC;
